 Movie: has a title, description and category

- Movie should have all standard REST actions

- Users should be able to rate movies (once they are logged in)

- Rating is of the form 1 to 5 stars (as picture or icon please)

- Users should be able to create/edit/delete/rate movies (once they are logged in)

The starting page should be a list of all movies with full-text search with facets:

- category (for example Action, Drama etc.)

- average ratings (5 stars, 4 stars etc.)

- A user should be able to filter the movies when he clicks on a facet

- A user should be able to rate movies (without page reload)

- Pagination with 10 movies per page

The app should be built using Twitter-Bootstrap, BackboneJS, Rails, PostgreSQL.
